list.name: Default
list.comment: Changed dimension to dimensionX attribute in Strategy objects. Added dimensionY attribute. This change is made in order to provide support if the dimension of the battlefield changes in the future. Created getter and setter methods for these two new attributes

task.summary: Inizio creazione delle prime classi del dominio (ancora da rivedere)
Inserimento delle variabili e dei metodi all'interno della classe BattleField; Eliminazione di alcuni namespace superflui
Utilities package created and Autoloader class added, created a main.php file for testing purposes.
Fixed battlefield matrix creation and updated constructor
Minor edits for the buildField function, static counter for shipID added
Implemented a rudimental version of the PlaceShip method. Added an array of Weapons inside Ship Objects.
Implemented 3 basic RangeStrategy objects: Single Square, Three Square (horizontal) and Four Square (squared). Implemented RangeStrategyFactory and modified main.php to do some testing

Changed dimension to dimensionX attribute in Strategy objects. Added dimensionY attribute. This change is made in order to provide support if the dimension of the battlefield changes in the future. Created getter and setter methods for these two new attributes
